Lazymux is python based tool in this tool and collection a of tools for termux users.
You can easily install some tools by typing number in the easiest way.This tool is especially for lazy people..ðŸ™ƒ

installation :

$ apt update 

$ apt upgrade

$ apt install git

$ apt install python2

$ git clone https://github.com/Gameye98/Lazymux

$ cd Lazymux 

$ chmod +X *

usage :

$ python2 lazymux.py

Now simply type the number of tool to install that particular tool in termux
